- Cow's.
- I'll just take a black, thanks.

07:45.567 --> 07:48.608
So, you are gonna have
my desk, when I'm gone.

07:48.692 --> 07:52.028
O'Shea here will tell you, with half the
island leaving for the show on Dungary,

07:52.029 --> 07:53.316
it'll be dead this weekend.

07:53.399 --> 07:56.066
- I'm sure I'll find something to do.
- Sure you will.

07:56.149 --> 07:58.899
- Here you go now.
- Thanks.

08:03.815 --> 08:07.148
- She really necessary?
- Do tell me, boy.

08:07.231 --> 08:10.231
You are only gone two weeks.
I can handle two weeks.

08:10.315 --> 08:12.065
You could, but you wouldn't!

08:29.354 --> 08:31.469
Tadhg, take a look at this.

08:34.470 --> 08:35.687
It's a big 'un.

08:35.770 --> 08:39.437
- That's not a lobster.
- Then what is it?

08:42.937 --> 08:47.852
Feck! You bastard, you! Paddy!
You knew it was going to do that.

08:47.936 --> 08:49.786
I didn't, on me life.

08:49.787 --> 08:52.686
Ugh! The smell!

08:52.769 --> 08:55.935
- What is it?
- 'Tis no fekkin' lobster!

